{"tid":1681021,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"午後數學題 2","createTime":"2019-10-29T07:05:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T08:59:31.000Z","uid":184509,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f8c7b150da6643befd23b5c76980354195639da7","tid":1681021,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:05:31.000Z","msg":"有四個學生A-D，佢地要做一個運氣test，個test以10分為滿分，而家要隨機generate 1至10其中一個整數比每個人作為佢地既分數，而且合格(Pass)既所需分數亦都係1至10隨機gen出黎既一個整數。結果出爐之後，會將所有學生既分數由高至低順序排列，如果遇上同分則會隨機排序(e.g. AB同分既話A唔一定係B上面)，最終得出以下排行，但果3個問號係唔小心被人塗走左既數據。咁到底Student D係Pass既機會係等於、大於定細於1/2呢？<br />\nStudent C：9 (Pass)<br />\nStudent B：? (Pass)<br />\nStudent D：? (?)<br />\nStudent A：7 (Fail)"},{"pid":"405366a6af6ef5a2b449d2d76e950dd154f9dc9d","tid":1681021,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:05:47.000Z","msg":"$1交稅攬炒機械人小測成績表已出！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679773\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1679773</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26833834f4b95fc654f1408cf71740d9290c73c","tid":1681021,"uid":190221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7kDwBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7kDwBC.jpg&h=6da1c92c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mtm3RDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtm3RDU.jpg&h=fd9c9c47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d59a246374b2f0910d619e548f95b58ae1bbbad","tid":1681021,"uid":136893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:09:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反思行動及行動數量<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（極緊急！！！）等我教大家點再引發群眾熱情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680895</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"68259d65a115fa7051d64312e7f950128b8a09f5","tid":1681021,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:12:51.000Z","msg":"大於<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa60aef7490951fc6dc97914c02d51ddae28201","tid":1681021,"uid":325046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:14:03.000Z","msg":"小於"},{"pid":"1b56aa677c3897380ca70d28e9f39e8a5ca02ddd","tid":1681021,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:14:24.000Z","msg":"等於"},{"pid":"0797a53dab23b4aa5c8a904f25ef2f16070810ec","tid":1681021,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68259d65a115fa7051d64312e7f950128b8a09f5","tid":1681021,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:12:51.000Z","msg":"大於<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:17:58.000Z","msg":"睇錯野，小於"},{"pid":"99006005045346ae7d0acad60f4a67492a0ec8f1","tid":1681021,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0797a53dab23b4aa5c8a904f25ef2f16070810ec","tid":1681021,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68259d65a115fa7051d64312e7f950128b8a09f5","tid":1681021,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:12:51.000Z","msg":"大於<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:17:58.000Z","msg":"睇錯野，小於"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:20:13.000Z","msg":"如果小於咁個Prob係幾多呢"},{"pid":"d3c0014721ce8922bfa160f11bd0b1236111b5a3","tid":1681021,"uid":32828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:20:17.000Z","msg":"等於 for sure<br />\n一係pass 一係唔pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1292ef126e706b9f067328109cf83d0f29cfd14","tid":1681021,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99006005045346ae7d0acad60f4a67492a0ec8f1","tid":1681021,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0797a53dab23b4aa5c8a904f25ef2f16070810ec","tid":1681021,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68259d65a115fa7051d64312e7f950128b8a09f5","tid":1681021,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:12:51.000Z","msg":"大於<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:17:58.000Z","msg":"睇錯野，小於"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:20:13.000Z","msg":"如果小於咁個Prob係幾多呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:27:38.000Z","msg":"11/24？"},{"pid":"e85385ef5068612dc50a948733cd664152df206a","tid":1681021,"uid":302878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:32:42.000Z","msg":"1/2？"},{"pid":"7b6f2a729bb0907b949f184bca4457acc522f2b8","tid":1681021,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:33:20.000Z","msg":"Student C：9 (Pass)<br />\nStudent B：? (Pass)<br />\nStudent D：? (?)<br />\nStudent A：7 (Fail)<br />\n<br />\nStudent B可以8分，可以9分<br />\n但9分既話佢只有1/2機會可以排喺C之後<br />\n所以8分既機會率係50%/(50%+50%*50%)=2/3<br />\n8分既機會率係25%/(50%+50%*50%)=1/3<br />\nCase 1: Student B有8分<br />\nStudent D一係7分(Fail) ，一係8分(Pass)<br />\n因為7分同8分都各有50%排喺B之後/A之前<br />\n所以合格機率係50%<br />\nCase 2: Student B有9分<br />\nStudent D可以係7分，8分，9分<br />\n7分既話佢有1/2機會排喺A之前<br />\n8分既話佢有1/2機會合格(合格分一係8分，一係9分)<br />\n9分既話佢有1/3機會排喺C同B之後<br />\n7分既機會率係(1/3)*(1/2)/((1/3)*(1/2)+(1/3)*(1/2)+(1/3)*(1/3))=0.375<br />\n8分既機會率係(1/3)*(1/2)/((1/3)*(1/2)+(1/3)*(1/2)+(1/3)*(1/3))=0.375<br />\n9分既機會率係(1/3)*(1/3)/((1/3)*(1/2)+(1/3)*(1/2)+(1/3)*(1/3))=0.25<br />\n所以合格機率係0.375*0.5+0.25=0.4375<br />\n<br />\n總合格機率係(2/3)*0.5+(1/3)*0.4375=0.479"},{"pid":"5c56abac7079968129f9ba31d5eae52725a272ab","tid":1681021,"uid":100412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p