e":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:20:13.000Z","msg":"如果小於咁個Prob係幾多呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:33:46.000Z","msg":"題目只係問大於、等於定小於<br />\n係咪即係唔使求個概率嘅實際數字呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"要呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔小心發表左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:37:09.000Z","msg":"功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76fb9df8f648817905305b0805187e1658409c2","tid":1681021,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:37:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Student C：9 (Pass)<br />\nStudent B：? (Pass)<br />\nStudent D：? (?)<br />\nStudent A：7 (Fail)<br />\n<br />\nStudent B可以8分，可以9分<br />\n但9分既話佢只有1/2機會可以排喺C之後<br />\n所以8分既機會率係50%/(50%+50%*50%)=2/3<br />\n8分既機會率係25%/(50%+50%*50%)=1/3<br />\nCase 1: Student B有8分<br />\nStudent D一係7分(Fail) ，一係8分(Pass)<br />\n因為7分同8分都各有50%排喺B之後/A之前<br />\n所以合格機率係50%<br />\nCase 2: Student B有9分<br />\nStudent D可以係7分，8分，9分<br />\n7分既話佢有1/2機會排喺A之前<br />\n8分既話佢有1/2機會合格(合格分一係8分，一係9分)<br />\n9分既話佢有1/3機會排喺C同B之後<br />\n7分既機會率係(1/3)*(1/2)/((1/3)*(1/2)+(1/3)+(1/3)*(1/3))=3/11<br />\n8分既機會率係(1/3)/((1/3)*(1/2)+(1/3)*(1/2)+(1/3)*(1/3))=6/11<br />\n9分既機會率係(1/3)*(1/3)/((1/3)*(1/2)+(1/3)*(1/2)+(1/3)*(1/3))=2/11<br />\n所以合格機率係(6/11)*0.5+(2/11)=5/11<br />\n<br />\n總合格機率係(2/3)*0.5+(1/3)*(5/11)=0.485</blockquote><br />\n改左"},{"pid":"961ae1c362a3941f872ba2f749acc4f63a375e64","tid":1681021,"uid":100412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3dcc03d47de93e68f77b611c04eae085d8bc872","tid":1681021,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c56abac7079968129f9ba31d5eae52725a272ab","tid":1681021,"uid":100412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99006005045346ae7d0acad60f4a67492a0ec8f1","tid":1681021,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"rep